---
title: Basil Pesto, Bacon & Pumpkin Risotto with Almond Pangrattato & Parsley
description: This rich, creamy risotto comes together in the oven, leaving you free to create a quick and crunchy almonds pangrattato to
sprinkle over at the end. Such a small factor takes this pumpkin and bacon meal to the next level – taste it and see!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/648138905555c0d634275bc0-ffb5a8ae.jpeg
